original_title: This is Ultimate Wrestling: Cactus Jack - No Holds Barred
overview: See Mick Foley, best-selling author and wrestling champion in some of the best grudge matches from the early years of his career. Single matches and tag-team warfare make this program a must for all wrestling fans. Rough, tough and unstoppable, the dastardly and devastating Cactus Jack became a hardcore legend.
title: This is Ultimate Wrestling: Cactus Jack - No Holds Barred
